---
import Page from "../../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page
  title="MCP Servers | Botify Life"
  description="Discover how easy, fast, and reliable it is to create MCP Servers with Botify Life."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-6 text-center">
      Effortless MCP Server Creation with Botify Life
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Building and managing MCP Servers with Botify Life is simple,
      lightning-fast, and highly reliable. Our intuitive platform empowers you
      to launch, scale, and monitor your servers in just a few clicks—no
      technical expertise required.
    </p>
    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <li
        class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">Instant Setup</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm"
          >Deploy your MCP Server in minutes with our streamlined process.</span
        >
      </li>
      <li
        class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">Reliable & Secure</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm"
          >Enjoy enterprise-grade reliability and robust security for all your
          workloads.</span
        >
      </li>
      <li
        class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1"
          >Scalable Performance</span
        >
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm"
          >Easily scale resources up or down as your needs change—no downtime.</span
        >
      </li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Python & Node.js Section with solid background -->
    <section
      class="w-full rounded-2xl bg-[#151c28] py-12 px-6 md:px-12 mb-12 shadow-lg flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10"
    >
      <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-start mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <h2
          class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <i class="fa-brands fa-python text-yellow-400"></i>
          <span>Python</span>
          <span class="mx-2 text-white font-normal">|</span>
          <i class="fa-brands fa-node-js text-green-400"></i>
          <span>Node.js</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-lg mb-4">
          Build, deploy, and manage your MCP Servers using your favorite
          language. Botify Life supports both Python and Node.js, making
          automation accessible for every developer.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-1 pl-2">
          <li>Ready-to-use SDKs for Python and Node.js</li>
          <li>Easy API integration for fast development</li>
          <li>Comprehensive docs and code samples</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a
        href="/signup"
        class="inline-block px-8 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
      >
        Get Started with MCP Servers
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Page>
